narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This course helped me to hone my independent working skills and to set/accomplish productive goals for myself.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The main strength was the free structure of the course. It was the student's responsibility to set goals for herself and to keep working throughout the course. Different students' prospectus ideas were in different stages throughout, and the course's flexibility allowed for each one to customize their workload to focus on the most productive tasks for each of them individually.
